data.description:
This home has so much to offer!

Sitting on a large corner lot within the quiet Remington Point neighborhood, 5808 Bridal Trail boasts over 2600 sq ft of living space including 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, walk in closets, an upstairs flex space, upstairs laundry, downstairs office with french doors, newer paint, new windows, huge covered patio with bar in backyard, new roof installed August 2023, and more. The community also includes multiple pools, parks, playground, and nearby schools, all while just a short drive away from Interstate-820. 

Come visit, love, make an offer, make new memories.
